node.text: Teaching is hard. Really hard. Sundays can be especially stressful as educators gear up for the week. The purpose of the Stress Less Sunday for Educators series will be to help educators be in the best mental space possible for the upcoming week!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by TeacherGoals on August 03, 2021. Coming to school when you're sick or need a mental break doesn't deserve applause. Including others, sharing a lunch with someone hungry, and not bullying others absolutely deserves recognition'.
